<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Anglo year earnings up 23 pct.</title>
<headline>Anglo year earnings up 23 pct.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-06-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended March 31</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
<p>Shr, (cts)</p>
<p>    - headline		2,144	 vs 1,746</p>
<p>    - total net	     3,037	 vs 1,885</p>
<p>    Div (cts)		   700	 vs   570</p>
<p>Full name: Anglo American Corp of South Africa Ltd</p>
<p>NOTE - Analysts polled by Reuters had forecast a consensus EPS of 2,220.5, within a range 2,165-2,294, and a year dividend of 690, within a range 680-700.  </p>
